6 NU and some specific modes
****************************

term is perfectly usable with nu-mode.  Just press Control+Space then
Control+c to run a sigstop.  Or, Control+Space then Control+b to open
another buffer.  The vanilla x keymap is used.  As of today there is no
prompt however.


